    {
      "id": "r2xMsgOxJfpS0pn2BhN_Z",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 386.2467956542969,
      "y": 4479.500129699707,
      "width": 759.0994873046875,
      "height": 575,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4i",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1432600330,
      "version": 470,
      "versionNonce": 2132059914,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781804496979,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. AI Scavenger Hunt\n    For 24 hours, keep a log of every time you think\n    AI might be involved in something you use or see. \n    Try to find at least 5 examples. \n    Write them down with a sentence explaining how AI helps there.\n\n2. AI or Not AI?\n    Look at these 5 technologies and decide: Does AI power it?\n        1. A basic alarm clock\n        2. Netflix recommendations\n        3. A door that opens when you push it\n        4. Autocorrect on a phone\n        5. A microwave timer\n    Write YES or NO and explain each.\n\n3. My AI Day\n    Write a short paragraph: \n    “In one day, AI helped me...” Use at least 3 real examples from your life.\n\n⭐ Bonus Challenge\nThink of one area of your life where you wish AI existed but it doesn’t yet. \nDescribe what it would do and how it would help you.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. AI Scavenger Hunt\n    For 24 hours, keep a log of every time you think\n    AI might be involved in something you use or see. \n    Try to find at least 5 examples. \n    Write them down with a sentence explaining how AI helps there.\n\n2. AI or Not AI?\n    Look at these 5 technologies and decide: Does AI power it?\n        1. A basic alarm clock\n        2. Netflix recommendations\n        3. A door that opens when you push it\n        4. Autocorrect on a phone\n        5. A microwave timer\n    Write YES or NO and explain each.\n\n3. My AI Day\n    Write a short paragraph: \n    “In one day, AI helped me...” Use at least 3 real examples from your life.\n\n⭐ Bonus Challenge\nThink of one area of your life where you wish AI existed but it doesn’t yet. \nDescribe what it would do and how it would help you.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
