      "versionNonce": 2110264915,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782286668300,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ANTIGRAVITY PROMPT — type this exactly, then press Enter\nWrite a Python script that:\n1. Has a CONFIG section with the Groq API key, model name llama3-8b-8192,\n    and max_tokens 250\n2. Has a SYSTEM_PROMPT that says: You are a content writer. \n    Write a short, clear paragraph about whatever topic the user gives you.\n3. Loops forever, asking the user to type a topic using input()\n4. If the user types 'exit', print 'Session ended' and stop\n5. Otherwise, send the topic to the AI and print the paragraph it writes\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ANTIGRAVITY PROMPT — type this exactly, then press Enter\nWrite a Python script that:\n1. Has a CONFIG section with the Groq API key, model name llama3-8b-8192,\n    and max_tokens 250\n2. Has a SYSTEM_PROMPT that says: You are a content writer. \n    Write a short, clear paragraph about whatever topic the user gives you.\n3. Loops forever, asking the user to type a topic using input()\n4. If the user types 'exit', print 'Session ended' and stop\n5. Otherwise, send the topic to the AI and print the paragraph it writes\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
