      "text": "–        Groq may cap temperature at 2.0 — if you get\nan API error above that, note it: 'the API itself\nenforces a limit'",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "–        Groq may cap temperature at 2.0 — if you get an API error above that, note it: 'the API itself enforces a limit'",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "UNh4UgEcPsqmh2GPl603a",
      "type": "text",
