      "text": "What is AI/LLM",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "B7XELzxrPdDkDvOaMuv1p",
      "originalText": "What is AI/LLM",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "g65GGmPprM0_pXR87LzDV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 372.800048828125,
      "y": 1706.5000381469727,
      "width": 832.3837280273438,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6k",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 909312477,
      "version": 133,
      "versionNonce": 756465789,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782325125283,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Is AI and LLM same thing?\nDoes an AI model search the internet every time it answers?\nDo AI really think?\nWhat is a token, and why is a token not always a word?\nWhy do AI tools have a context window?\nHow does AI decide which word comes next?",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Is AI and LLM same thing?\nDoes an AI model search the internet every time it answers?\nDo AI really think?\nWhat is a token, and why is a token not always a word?\nWhy do AI tools have a context window?\nHow does AI decide which word comes next?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
