      "text": "Anatomy of a Correct Prompt",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "X7R8uzQ2slqwJACSSJhPn",
      "originalText": "Anatomy of a Correct Prompt",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GJ0s4IFHPuc4Ij5IGZdbV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 402.7998466491699,
      "y": 2383.700183868408,
      "width": 770.0277099609375,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1584282259,
      "version": 151,
      "versionNonce": 339615763,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782327138540,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "THE FIVE PARTS OF A CORRECT PROMPT\n\n• Context — what world is the AI operating in. \n• Task — one clear verb, one clear action \n• Input — the actual data or specifics you're handing it\n• Constraints — what you don't want: \n• Format — exactly how you want the answer back\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "THE FIVE PARTS OF A CORRECT PROMPT\n\n• Context — what world is the AI operating in. \n• Task — one clear verb, one clear action \n• Input — the actual data or specifics you're handing it\n• Constraints — what you don't want: \n• Format — exactly how you want the answer back\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
