      "seed": 346577277,
      "version": 80,
      "versionNonce": 1673677981,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782327344256,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Context:\nYou are a financial data analyst helping a beginner understand Indian equity price movement.\n\nTask:\nCompare the stock’s performance across the two periods and identify the main trend.\n\nInput:\nStock: Reliance Industries\nPeriod 1: 1 January 2026 to 31 March 2026\nPeriod 2: 1 April 2026 to 30 June 2026\nPrice change in Period 1: ₹1,250 to ₹1,340\nPrice change in Period 2: ₹1,340 to ₹1,290\nVolume: Higher in Period 2 than Period 1\n\nConstraints:\nDo not give buy, sell, or hold advice.\nDo not predict future prices.\nUse simple language and explain any financial term in brackets.\n\nFormat:\nGive the answer in a table with these columns:\nPeriod | Price Movement | Trend | Simple Explanation\nThen add a 2-sentence overall summary.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Context:\nYou are a financial data analyst helping a beginner understand Indian equity price movement.\n\nTask:\nCompare the stock’s performance across the two periods and identify the main trend.\n\nInput:\nStock: Reliance Industries\nPeriod 1: 1 January 2026 to 31 March 2026\nPeriod 2: 1 April 2026 to 30 June 2026\nPrice change in Period 1: ₹1,250 to ₹1,340\nPrice change in Period 2: ₹1,340 to ₹1,290\nVolume: Higher in Period 2 than Period 1\n\nConstraints:\nDo not give buy, sell, or hold advice.\nDo not predict future prices.\nUse simple language and explain any financial term in brackets.\n\nFormat:\nGive the answer in a table with these columns:\nPeriod | Price Movement | Trend | Simple Explanation\nThen add a 2-sentence overall summary.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
