      "updated": 1782345452507,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Using the last 10 trading days of daily OHLC data for RELIANCE.NS,\nidentify whether the stock is in an uptrend, downtrend, or trading\nrange, and explain your reasoning in 3 bullet points. Do not make a\nbuy or sell recommendation.\"\n",
