      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Using the last 10 trading days of daily OHLC data for RELIANCE.NS,\nidentify whether the stock is in an uptrend, downtrend, or trading\nrange, and explain your reasoning in 3 bullet points. Do not make a\nbuy or sell recommendation.\"\n",
