    {
      "id": "Ja0rsNEGogaHuhGO7X25Q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 289.56123477910285,
      "y": 4894.664964157042,
      "width": 976.94775390625,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7S",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1795278045,
      "version": 84,
      "versionNonce": 1474019283,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782345592441,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• We added 'do not make a buy or sell recommendation' as a constraint \n   — what's a different constraint you'd want for your own use case, \n   and why?\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• We added 'do not make a buy or sell recommendation' as a constraint \n   — what's a different constraint you'd want for your own use case, \n   and why?\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tm1tBAO_MU67PQwORR2OH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 296.9803842753484,
      "y": 5047.538375121479,
      "width": 898.379638671875,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7T",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1216876285,
      "version": 134,
      "versionNonce": 267478931,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782345595790,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• If the AI ignored our format instruction and gave five bullets \n  instead of three, is that a prompting failure or a model failure? \n  How would you fix it?",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• If the AI ignored our format instruction and gave five bullets \n  instead of three, is that a prompting failure or a model failure? \n  How would you fix it?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
