      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1504937491,
      "version": 31,
      "versionNonce": 1926199827,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782345707783,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• Now that you've seen the before/after, could you rewrite this \nprompt to ask for a comparison between two stocks instead of one? \nWhat would actually have to change?",
