      "seed": 1268673843,
      "version": 197,
      "versionNonce": 939328413,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782345989350,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• The agent decided on its own to use the yfinance library — \nwe never told it to. \nWhat does that tell you about 'agent' versus just 'autocomplete'?",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• The agent decided on its own to use the yfinance library — \nwe never told it to. \nWhat does that tell you about 'agent' versus just 'autocomplete'?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9wMggLsD3lkZ-hgoiQ6Y-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 179.05507695765226,
      "y": 6399.579686951187,
      "width": 1022.3076782226562,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1147563197,
      "version": 73,
      "versionNonce": 1881844861,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782346025937,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• If this script had pulled the wrong company's data from a ticker mix-up, \nat what point would you actually have caught it?",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• If this script had pulled the wrong company's data from a ticker mix-up, \nat what point would you actually have caught it?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
