      "text": "Context: I want to turn this fixed-ticker chart into something\nreusable for any stock.\nTask: Let the user choose what to look at, instead of it being\nhardcoded to one stock.\nInput: Add a text input for the stock ticker and a date range\npicker, both feeding into the existing chart logic.\nFormat: The chart should redraw automatically whenever the ticker\nor date range changes — no extra button click needed.\nConstraint: Keep the defaults as RELIANCE.NS and the last 6 months,\nso the app still works immediately on load.\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Context: I want to turn this fixed-ticker chart into something\nreusable for any stock.\nTask: Let the user choose what to look at, instead of it being\nhardcoded to one stock.\nInput: Add a text input for the stock ticker and a date range\npicker, both feeding into the existing chart logic.\nFormat: The chart should redraw automatically whenever the ticker\nor date range changes — no extra button click needed.\nConstraint: Keep the defaults as RELIANCE.NS and the last 6 months,\nso the app still works immediately on load.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
