      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782347148572,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• Could you go the other way — feed AI a paragraph of commentary and get structured \nnumbers back out? What would that even mean?",
      "fontSize": 28,
